      <h1 style="font-weight:normal">logline in a nutshell</h1>
      <hr>
      <p><strong>logline</strong> helps teams of all shapes and sizes — such as startups, NGOs and scientists — produce high-quality, readable docs. </p>
      <h2 id="why-logline-">Why logline?</h2>
      <p>Great writing is a force multiplier for any organization, but many teams find it hard to produce quality writing when they need it most. <strong>logline</strong> was founded to provide <em>flexible</em>, high-quality writing services for these teams. We set high standards for writing style, economy and readability. We are not an agency, so there is no middleman between you and your writer. This makes coordination flexible and lightweight, while it also helps to keep project costs down.</p>
      <p>Our projects range from software documentation to meeting minutes, financial reports and conference summaries. </p>


